hands_on_practices.solution:
极坐标下的度规为
$$g_{rr}=1,\quad g_{\theta\theta}=r^2,\qquad \sqrt{|g|}=r.$$ 
升指标可得
$$T^{rr}=g^{rr}g^{rr}T_{rr}=T_{rr}=\alpha r^k,$$ 
$$T^{\theta\theta}=g^{\theta\theta}g^{\theta\theta}T_{\theta\theta}=\frac1{r^4}\,\beta r^{k+2}=\beta r^{k-2}.$$ 
使用恒等式
$$\nabla_\mu T^{\mu r}=\frac1{\sqrt{|g|}}\partial_\mu\bigl(\sqrt{|g|}\,T^{\mu r}\bigr)+\Gamma^r_{\mu\lambda}T^{\mu\lambda},$$ 
我们只有对 $r$ 的导数项和非零的克里斯托费尔符号项：
$$\frac1r\partial_r\bigl(rT^{rr}\bigr)
=\frac1r\partial_r\bigl(\alpha r^{k+1}\bigr)
=\alpha(k+1)r^{k-1},$$
$$\Gamma^r_{\theta\theta}=-r\;\Longrightarrow\;
\Gamma^r_{\mu\lambda}T^{\mu\lambda}
=\Gamma^r_{\theta\theta}T^{\theta\theta}
=-r\cdot\beta r^{k-2}
=-\beta r^{k-1}.$$ 
将这些项相加可得
$$F^r=\nabla_\mu T^{\mu r}
=\alpha(k+1)r^{k-1}-\beta r^{k-1}
=\bigl[\alpha(k+1)-\beta\bigr]r^{k-1}.$$
